coolest in Tokyo, huh?

00:00:54.989 --> 00:00:57.959 position:21% line:5% align:start
Well my Zephyr's the
best in all o' Japan.

00:00:57.992 --> 00:00:59.894 position:13% line:5% align:start
(motorcycle engine revving)

00:00:59.928 --> 00:01:01.663 position:44% line:5% align:start
