got worth fightin' about

00:01:16.143 --> 00:01:19.179 position:13% line:83% align:start
when you're all still
stuck here on planet Earth?

00:01:19.212 --> 00:01:22.416 position:21% line:5% align:start
My Rocket's the best
bike in the universe!

00:01:22.449 --> 00:01:24.451 position:13% line:5% align:start
(motorcycle engine revving)

00:01:24.484 --> 00:01:28.188 position:7% line:5% align:start
