finally grew some pubes eh?

00:01:28.221 --> 00:01:30.090 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Draken] Huh, look
who's talkin'.

00:01:30.123 --> 00:01:33.460 position:19% line:83% align:start
Whoa I'm getting
really sleepy. (sighs)

00:01:35.063 --> 00:01:36.598 position:13% line:89% align:start
(motorcycle engine revving)

00:01:36.631 --> 00:01:37.799 position:44% line:5% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:01:37.832 --> 00:01:40.635 position:10% line:5% align:start
My CBX400F's the best of all!

00:01:40.668 --> 00:01:42.135 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's a race to the shrine!

00:01:42.870 --> 00:01:45.439 position:27% line:83% align:start
Damn you, that's
not a fair race!

00:01:45.472 --> 00:01:47.675 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's cheating and you
damn well know it, Pah!

00:01:47.709 --> 00:01:49.443 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll beat you anyway!

00:01:49.476 --> 00:01:52.647 position:19% line:83% align:start
Last one there's gonna
get his ass kicked!

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:53.848 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Mikey snoring)

00:01:53.881 --> 00:01:55.349 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hey, What the hell are you doing

00:01:55.382 --> 00:01:57.250 position:19% line:89% align:start
falling asleep, Mikey?

00:01:57.284 --> 00:01:59.654 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wake up, you're gonna
fall off, you dumbass!

00:01:59.687 --> 00:02:01.221 position:30% line:89% align:start
Mikey, wake up!

00:02:03.223 --> 00:02:08.161 position:21% line:89% align:start
(opening theme music)

00:03:36.718 --> 00:03:39.252 position:30% line:5% align:start
(Baji groaning)

00:03:43.157 --> 00:03:44.357 position:38% line:89% align:start
Damn it!

00:03:49.597 --> 00:03:51.966 position:7% line:89% align:start
Thanks a lot for all the help.

00:03:51.999 --> 00:03:53.601 position:21% line:89% align:start
Took ya long enough.

00:03:53.634 --> 00:03:54.802 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're dead last.

00:03:54.836 --> 00:03:56.504 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's not my fault,

00:03:56.537 --> 00:03:59.272 position:10% line:83% align:start
he was dead asleep on my back
the whole time, passed out!

00:03:59.306 --> 00:04:02.309 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Excuses much?
-Yeah, pretty lame, dude.

00:04:02.342 --> 00:04:03.811 position:21% line:89% align:start
Easy for you to say!

00:04:03.845 --> 00:04:06.346 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hm, are we here?

00:04:06.379 --> 00:04:08.950 position:16% line:83% align:start
So what'd you want to
talk to us about, Mikey?

00:04:12.486 --> 00:04:15.322 position:10% line:83% align:start
There's a gang called the
Black Dragons, heard of 'em?

00:04:16.456 --> 00:04:17.692 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah I've heard of 'em

00:04:17.725 --> 00:04:19.861 position:19% line:83% align:start
and I also heard that
they're brutal as hell.

00:04:19.894 --> 00:04:21.562 position:13% line:89% align:start
Three years older than us.

00:04:21.596 --> 00:04:22.597 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:04:25.298 --> 00:04:27.969 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why didn't you come and
talk to us, Kazutora?

00:04:30.138 --> 00:04:32.607 position:24% line:83% align:start
Instead I had to
hear it from Baji.

00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:34.075 position:21% line:83% align:start
You've been fighting
the Black Dragons

00:04:34.108 --> 00:04:35.543 position:16% line:89% align:start
on your own, haven't you?

00:04:35.576 --> 00:04:38.278 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Takashi] What? Kazutora got
into it with the Black Dragons?

00:04:38.311 --> 00:04:39.279 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:04:39.312 --> 00:04:40.782 position:27% line:89% align:start
He can't help it.

00:04:40.815 --> 00:04:44.317 position:7% line:83% align:start
I guess Kazutora lives right
inside the Black Dragons' turf

00:04:44.351 --> 00:04:46.486 position:19% line:89% align:start
I see what's happening.

00:04:46.521 --> 00:04:48.689 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey, Wait a minute, you're
not planning to throw down

00:04:48.723 --> 00:04:51.559 position:19% line:83% align:start
against the Black
Dragons are you, Mikey?

00:04:51.592 --> 00:04:52.527 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yup.

00:04:53.895 --> 00:04:56.831 position:13% line:83% align:start
But these guys are the
real deal, that's for sure.

00:04:56.864 --> 00:04:59.299 position:19% line:83% align:start
So we're gonna need a
good reason to do this.

00:05:01.536 --> 00:05:04.172 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, I've got an idea.

00:05:04.205 --> 00:05:06.306 position:21% line:83% align:start
Let's just start our
own gang, you guys!

00:05:06.339 --> 00:05:09.143 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-A biker gang, just us?

00:05:09.177 --> 00:05:10.310 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hell yeah!

00:05:10.343 --> 00:05:11.579 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:05:11.612 --> 00:05:14.414 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey, that sounds good to me.

00:05:14.447 --> 00:05:16.851 position:16% line:83% align:start
And we already know
everyone's position too.

00:05:18.451 --> 00:05:20.320 position:21% line:83% align:start
Our commander's gonna
be the invincible,

00:05:20.353 --> 00:05:22.089 position:16% line:89% align:start
cocky little shit, Mikey!

00:05:22.123 --> 00:05:24.457 position:13% line:89% align:start
Aw, you're making me blush.

00:05:24.491 --> 00:05:25.993 position:10% line:89% align:start
Our vice commander's gonna be

00:05:26.027 --> 00:05:28.395 position:7% line:89% align:start
our dependable big bro, Draken!

00:05:29.664 --> 00:05:33.000 position:7% line:83% align:start
Our mediator, Takashi Mitsuya,
will command our elite guard!

00:05:34.367 --> 00:05:37.404 position:19% line:83% align:start
Our powerhouse, Pah,
will carry our banner!

00:05:37.437 --> 00:05:40.407 position:19% line:83% align:start
And alongside me as our
attack unit, Kazutora.

00:05:44.045 --> 00:05:48.249 position:19% line:83% align:start
Okay, but guys, are you
sure you wanna do this?

00:05:48.282 --> 00:05:50.952 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've already decided
on our new gang's name.

00:05:50.985 --> 00:05:52.587 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Yeah, what is it, dude?
-Huh?

00:05:52.620 --> 00:05:55.723 position:5% line:89% align:start
We'll be the Tokyo Manjiro Gang!

00:05:55.756 --> 00:05:56.624 position:30% line:89% align:start
[All] So lame!

00:05:57.558 --> 00:05:58.993 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well that's a stupid name.

00:05:59.026 --> 00:06:00.393 position:19% line:89% align:start
But on the bright side,

00:06:00.427 --> 00:06:02.597 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm definitely down with
the idea of starting a gang.

00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:04.732 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah, well that's a start.

00:06:04.765 --> 00:06:06.701 position:13% line:83% align:start
I guess your point is that
if we had our own gang

00:06:06.734 --> 00:06:08.536 position:21% line:83% align:start
then we'd have a good
reason to throw down

00:06:08.569 --> 00:06:11.739 position:19% line:83% align:start
with the Black Dragons,
even with a sucky name.

00:06:11.772 --> 00:06:12.807 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Mikey] Ouch!

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:14.976 position:19% line:83% align:start
Starting up a gang
sounds super exciting!

00:06:15.009 --> 00:06:16.844 position:16% line:89% align:start
But that name does suck.

00:06:16.878 --> 00:06:18.378 position:30% line:89% align:start
You guys suck!

00:06:18.411 --> 00:06:20.214 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, then I guess it's settled.

00:06:20.248 --> 00:06:21.448 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:25.186 --> 00:06:26.654 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:06:26.687 --> 00:06:30.258 position:16% line:83% align:start
We're willing to give you
everything that we've got.

00:06:30.291 --> 00:06:32.927 position:24% line:83% align:start
Create this new
age for us, Mikey.

00:06:36.264 --> 00:06:38.398 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:06:38.431 --> 00:06:40.368 position:21% line:83% align:start
What kind of gang do
you guys wanna have?

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.503 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hm, let's see...

00:06:43.671 --> 00:06:46.406 position:21% line:83% align:start
The kind that I want
is the kind of gang

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:48.809 position:16% line:83% align:start
where we can all risk
our lives for each other,

00:06:48.843 --> 00:06:50.011 position:27% line:89% align:start
every one of us!

00:06:52.613 --> 00:06:55.349 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey, let's buy some charms
to make this official!

00:06:55.383 --> 00:06:57.518 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Yeah, good idea!
-All right, let's do it!

00:07:04.491 --> 00:07:07.695 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey hurry up, you guys,
what're you waiting for?

00:07:07.728 --> 00:07:09.196 position:10% line:89% align:start
Come on before they run out!

00:07:14.402 --> 00:07:17.104 position:10% line:89% align:start
Damn, guys, that's expensive.

00:07:18.773 --> 00:07:20.107 position:38% line:89% align:start
313 yen.

00:07:20.141 --> 00:07:22.576 position:38% line:83% align:start
-50 yen.
-100 yen.

00:07:22.610 --> 00:07:25.212 position:38% line:83% align:start
-15 yen.
-25 yen.

00:07:25.246 --> 00:07:26.446 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takashi] 32 yen.

00:07:26.479 --> 00:07:28.582 position:27% line:89% align:start
(bikers sighing)

00:07:28.616 --> 00:07:31.819 position:10% line:83% align:start
Oh you gotta be shittin' me,
none of us can afford one!

00:07:31.852 --> 00:07:33.554 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, maybe not.

00:07:33.587 --> 00:07:36.524 position:16% line:83% align:start
But if we all pitch in,
we'll be able to buy one.

00:07:38.491 --> 00:07:39.492 position:27% line:89% align:start
(bikers gasping)

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:48.102 position:24% line:83% align:start
You should hold on
to it for us, Baji.

00:07:48.135 --> 00:07:49.570 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:07:49.603 --> 00:07:51.973 position:13% line:83% align:start
You're the reason we formed
the gang in the first place.

00:07:52.006 --> 00:07:53.374 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's good.

00:07:53.407 --> 00:07:54.875 position:19% line:89% align:start
Take care of it for us.

00:07:56.077 --> 00:07:58.512 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:08:02.216 --> 00:08:03.684 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'll take good care of it.

00:08:04.752 --> 00:08:07.989 position:7% line:89% align:start
Count on me, that's a promise.

00:08:08.022 --> 00:08:10.658 position:30% line:89% align:start
(somber music)

00:08:15.863 --> 00:08:18.866 position:24% line:83% align:start
And here it is,
this is the charm.

00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:24.438 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi sobbing)

00:08:24.472 --> 00:08:26.173 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm not the one
who created Toman.

00:08:28.142 --> 00:08:29.176 position:33% line:89% align:start
It was Baji.

00:08:32.713 --> 00:08:36.951 position:13% line:83% align:start
If one of us gets hurt,
the rest of us protect him.

00:08:36.984 --> 00:08:40.354 position:13% line:83% align:start
We wanted to be a gang
that protected one another.

00:08:40.388 --> 00:08:43.557 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's the kind of gang we
promised each other we would be.

00:08:46.727 --> 00:08:49.163 position:16% line:89% align:start
Baji was fighting, (sobs)

00:08:50.564 --> 00:08:52.633 position:24% line:83% align:start
fighting all on his
own this whole time!

00:08:52.666 --> 00:08:56.303 position:27% line:83% align:start
All to keep that
promise! (sniffs)

00:08:56.337 --> 00:08:59.540 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi sobbing)

00:09:02.209 --> 00:09:04.078 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry Baji, I failed.

00:09:11.819 --> 00:09:14.021 position:27% line:83% align:start
-(sirens blaring)
-Uh oh.

00:09:14.055 --> 00:09:15.589 position:30% line:89% align:start
Popo's coming.

00:09:15.623 --> 00:09:17.858 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come on, boys, we're outta here.

00:09:19.627 --> 00:09:20.795 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yo, ever'body out!

00:09:20.828 --> 00:09:22.329 position:16% line:89% align:start
Get lost, scatter, scram!

00:09:33.641 --> 00:09:35.776 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Kazutora] I'm gonna
stay with Baji.

00:09:35.810 --> 00:09:37.344 position:13% line:89% align:start
You should get out of here.

00:09:39.246 --> 00:09:40.648 position:30% line:89% align:start
Why, Kazutora?

00:09:41.782 --> 00:09:43.751 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm responsible for all of this.

00:09:44.618 --> 00:09:47.021 position:24% line:83% align:start
I want to be the
one to pay for it.

00:09:49.457 --> 00:09:50.724 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Mikey] All right then.

00:09:56.897 --> 00:09:58.866 position:7% line:89% align:start
Gotta go Toman, everybody out!

00:09:58.899 --> 00:10:00.301 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Got it, Draken.
-Right!

00:10:02.636 --> 00:10:05.072 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:10:06.774 --> 00:10:09.944 position:21% line:89% align:start
(gang member sobbing)

00:10:19.987 --> 00:10:20.788 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mikey!

00:10:22.656 --> 00:10:25.126 position:7% line:89% align:start
I know I can never be forgiven.

00:10:25.159 --> 00:10:28.762 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not about Shinichiro,
and not, about Baji.

00:10:30.264 --> 00:10:34.969 position:7% line:83% align:start
But it's a burden I'll have
to carry, the rest of my life.

00:10:36.337 --> 00:10:38.739 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:11:13.874 --> 00:11:17.144 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] On
October 31st, 2005

00:11:17.178 --> 00:11:20.781 position:24% line:83% align:start
