death, and one arrest.

00:11:31.859 --> 00:11:35.362 position:10% line:83% align:start
And eventually, the conflict
would come to be known as,

00:11:35.396 --> 00:11:36.897 position:21% line:89% align:start
The Bloody Halloween.

00:12:02.691 --> 00:12:05.159 position:19% line:83% align:start
I brought you some just
like you asked me to,

00:12:05.192 --> 00:12:05.993 position:30% line:89% align:start
it's still hot.

00:12:10.264 --> 00:12:12.199 position:16% line:89% align:start
Chifuyu, I could sure go

00:12:12.233 --> 00:12:14.902 position:24% line:83% align:start
for some Peyang
yakisoba about now.

00:12:16.737 --> 00:12:19.740 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's split it, kay?

00:12:22.443 --> 00:12:24.878 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's what we did the
first time we met, too.

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:27.281 position:33% line:89% align:start
We split it.

00:12:34.888 --> 00:12:36.757 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Teacher] Starting today,
and if you do well,

00:12:36.790 --> 00:12:38.125 position:16% line:89% align:start
for the next three years,

00:12:38.158 --> 00:12:40.060 position:21% line:83% align:start
