have the great honor

00:12:40.094 --> 00:12:41.762 position:21% line:83% align:start
to be students at
this esteemed school.

00:12:41.795 --> 00:12:43.163 position:24% line:89% align:start
(student grunting)

00:12:43.197 --> 00:12:45.667 position:13% line:83% align:start
I expect each and every one
of you to do your very best,

00:12:45.700 --> 00:12:46.867 position:24% line:89% align:start
(student grunting)

00:12:46.900 --> 00:12:48.802 position:21% line:83% align:start
in both academics and
in club activities.

00:12:48.836 --> 00:12:50.137 position:24% line:89% align:start
(student grunting)

00:12:50.170 --> 00:12:52.707 position:10% line:83% align:start
We trust that you will leave
here far more dignified

00:12:52.741 --> 00:12:55.376 position:16% line:83% align:start
and more respectful than
when you first came.

00:12:55.409 --> 00:12:58.779 position:24% line:89% align:start
(student groaning)

