Yeah well, respect
stuff's not happening,

00:13:01.815 --> 00:13:03.050 position:24% line:5% align:start
not even a little.

00:13:04.218 --> 00:13:06.353 position:24% line:83% align:start
'cause I'm the most
important guy here.

00:13:06.387 --> 00:13:08.956 position:33% line:89% align:start
(rock music)

00:13:09.923 --> 00:13:12.761 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're so freaking
awesome, Chifuyu!

00:13:12.793 --> 00:13:14.928 position:19% line:83% align:start
Teachers don't seem to
intimidate you at all.

00:13:14.962 --> 00:13:16.631 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, man, you could
probably take over

00:13:16.665 --> 00:13:18.465 position:27% line:83% align:start
the whole country
if you wanted to!

00:13:18.499 --> 00:13:22.236 position:5% line:83% align:start
You dumbass, I ain't
interested in any of that shit.

00:13:22.269 --> 00:13:25.839 position:16% line:83% align:start
The older delinquents are
all lame nowadays, anyway.

00:13:25.873 --> 00:13:27.875 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's why being one
isn't cool anymore.

00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:33.914 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:13:33.947 --> 00:13:37.151 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, Chifuyu, check
out what we just heard!

00:13:37.184 --> 00:13:38.285 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:13:38.319 --> 00:13:40.854 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's a new kid in Class
3 that got held back!

00:13:40.888 --> 00:13:42.323 position:19% line:89% align:start
And he's a first-year!

00:13:42.356 --> 00:13:46.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
Stop it, you can get
held back in junior high?

00:13:46.293 --> 00:13:47.227 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:13:47.261 --> 00:13:49.897 position:16% line:83% align:start
He's gotta be some insane
kind of delinquent!

00:13:49.930 --> 00:13:51.098 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, all right.

00:13:52.433 --> 00:13:54.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well then, guess I
better let him know

00:13:54.536 --> 00:13:56.236 position:13% line:89% align:start
who's the boss around here.

00:13:56.270 --> 00:13:57.905 position:7% line:89% align:start
Whoa, you don't leave any doubt

00:13:57.938 --> 00:14:00.107 position:19% line:83% align:start
about who's on top
here, do you, Chifuyu?

00:14:02.711 --> 00:14:03.911 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hey you.

00:14:05.112 --> 00:14:07.448 position:7% line:89% align:start
Which one's Baji, the new kid?

00:14:07.481 --> 00:14:09.450 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh.

00:14:09.483 --> 00:14:11.051 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh, that guy?

00:14:17.391 --> 00:14:18.859 position:33% line:83% align:start
-That's him?
-Yeah.

00:14:18.892 --> 00:14:20.127 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Seriously?

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:21.830 position:19% line:83% align:start
The four-eyes with
the slicked-back hair?

00:14:21.862 --> 00:14:22.831 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Student] Mm-hmm.

00:14:22.863 --> 00:14:24.733 position:7% line:89% align:start
They held back a guy like him?

00:14:24.766 --> 00:14:27.000 position:21% line:83% align:start
Betcha 100 yen his
parents made him quit

00:14:27.034 --> 00:14:28.469 position:16% line:89% align:start
to work as an errand boy.

00:14:28.503 --> 00:14:31.004 position:19% line:83% align:start
100 yen says he's a
scared lonely shut-in.

00:14:31.038 --> 00:14:32.674 position:13% line:89% align:start
10 says he just quit coming

00:14:32.707 --> 00:14:34.341 position:24% line:83% align:start
because he thought
school was stupid.

00:14:35.744 --> 00:14:38.445 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm outta here, this
is a waste of time.

00:14:56.631 --> 00:14:59.634 position:27% line:83% align:start
I see, so that's
what that means.

00:15:00.835 --> 00:15:02.136 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:15:02.169 --> 00:15:03.170 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:05.372 --> 00:15:06.140 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who're you?

00:15:06.173 --> 00:15:09.076 position:10% line:89% align:start
Chifuyu Matsuno from Class 1.

00:15:09.109 --> 00:15:10.911 position:13% line:89% align:start
Never heard've ya, Chifuyu.

00:15:11.780 --> 00:15:13.882 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Tell me, nerd.
-Huh?

00:15:13.914 --> 00:15:15.416 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu] What's
this s'posed to be?

00:15:15.449 --> 00:15:18.385 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Baji] That's
"Tora," for "tiger".

00:15:18.419 --> 00:15:19.754 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well it's wrong.

00:15:19.788 --> 00:15:21.021 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:15:21.054 --> 00:15:23.858 position:19% line:83% align:start
I coulda sworn I had
that one exactly right!

00:15:23.892 --> 00:15:24.859 position:30% line:89% align:start
What the hell?

00:15:24.893 --> 00:15:26.528 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why're you dressed like a nerd

00:15:26.561 --> 00:15:27.896 position:5% line:89% align:start
when you can't even write tiger?

00:15:27.928 --> 00:15:31.298 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tora, oh, this can't
happen, I can't go back!

00:15:31.331 --> 00:15:32.366 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Huh?

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:34.602 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't let them
hold me back again.

00:15:34.636 --> 00:15:36.403 position:19% line:89% align:start
It'd break Mom's heart!

00:15:36.437 --> 00:15:38.640 position:19% line:89% align:start
(chuckles) So serious.

00:15:43.711 --> 00:15:45.780 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is "tiger".

00:15:45.814 --> 00:15:47.181 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:15:47.214 --> 00:15:49.517 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey thank you,
you're a good guy!

00:15:49.551 --> 00:15:53.521 position:10% line:83% align:start
(chuckles) So, what's this
you're tryin' to write here?

00:15:53.555 --> 00:15:55.222 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Well it's, uh...
-Huh?

00:15:57.525 --> 00:15:58.292 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's a friendship letter.

00:15:58.325 --> 00:15:59.293 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:59.326 --> 00:16:00.762 position:13% line:89% align:start
To a pen pal, that's gross!

00:16:00.795 --> 00:16:03.798 position:7% line:83% align:start
You shut up! It's none of your
damn business who I write to!

00:16:03.832 --> 00:16:05.299 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'll murder you!

00:16:05.332 --> 00:16:08.101 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu] (chuckles )Okay
okay, hot-head, chill out.

00:16:08.135 --> 00:16:09.737 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh hey, you got
this one wrong too.

00:16:09.771 --> 00:16:11.004 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Baji] Huh? Seriously?

00:16:15.042 --> 00:16:18.479 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Friend] Yo, what're you
spacin' out about, Chifuyu?

00:16:18.513 --> 00:16:19.747 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Huh?

00:16:19.781 --> 00:16:22.584 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, I'm just still thinking
about that nerd I met.

00:16:22.617 --> 00:16:23.984 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Friend] Huh? Why?

00:16:24.017 --> 00:16:27.988 position:19% line:83% align:start
You'll forget about him
by tomorrow. (laughs)

00:16:31.024 --> 00:16:33.427 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Hey, Matsuno!
-Huh?

00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:35.763 position:27% line:89% align:start
(bikers laughing)

00:16:35.797 --> 00:16:37.297 position:21% line:89% align:start
Listen here, jackass,

00:16:37.331 --> 00:16:39.734 position:13% line:83% align:start
Where d'you get off
stompin' on my homeboy here

00:16:39.767 --> 00:16:41.068 position:13% line:89% align:start
without my permission, huh?

00:16:41.101 --> 00:16:43.938 position:16% line:83% align:start
Heh heh, you went an
pissed off the commander

00:16:43.972 --> 00:16:46.508 position:21% line:83% align:start
of the Mandala biker
gang, you idiot!

00:16:46.541 --> 00:16:47.976 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Gang Member]
You're finished now!

00:16:48.008 --> 00:16:49.176 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're gonna see what happens

00:16:49.209 --> 00:16:51.411 position:24% line:83% align:start
to anyone who
defies us, Matsuno!

00:16:53.113 --> 00:16:55.850 position:5% line:83% align:start
You are gonna learn some
manners and some respect today!

00:16:55.884 --> 00:16:57.785 position:13% line:89% align:start
And oh it's gonna hurt too!

00:16:58.620 --> 00:16:59.854 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:16:59.888 --> 00:17:02.189 position:33% line:89% align:start
(blow thuds)

00:17:02.222 --> 00:17:04.592 position:19% line:89% align:start
(gang leader groaning)

00:17:04.626 --> 00:17:06.628 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, I am so sorry!

00:17:06.661 --> 00:17:07.829 position:16% line:89% align:start
I was trying to greet you

00:17:07.862 --> 00:17:09.797 position:24% line:83% align:start
and I hit you with
my head instead.

00:17:10.899 --> 00:17:12.332 position:38% line:89% align:start
But you?

00:17:12.366 --> 00:17:14.301 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ambushing somebody
with eight against one?

00:17:14.334 --> 00:17:17.337 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hmph, biker gang, my ass!

00:17:19.373 --> 00:17:20.708 position:38% line:89% align:start
How lame.

00:17:20.742 --> 00:17:23.511 position:27% line:89% align:start
(bikers growling)

00:17:23.545 --> 00:17:28.550 position:19% line:83% align:start
-(blows thudding)
-(combatants grunting)

00:17:29.684 --> 00:17:32.587 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Gang Member] Kill him!

00:17:32.620 --> 00:17:35.222 position:27% line:89% align:start
(blows thudding)

00:17:36.390 --> 00:17:41.461 position:19% line:83% align:start
(gang members
laughing and taunting)

00:17:41.495 --> 00:17:44.431 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm not gonna be able to hold
out much longer on my own...

00:17:52.172 --> 00:17:54.742 position:19% line:83% align:start
End of the line, gonna
crack yer head open!

00:17:54.776 --> 00:17:56.143 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu Voiceover] Oh shit!

00:17:57.011 --> 00:17:59.013 position:10% line:89% align:start
Eight of you against one kid?

00:17:59.047 --> 00:18:01.081 position:21% line:83% align:start
And armed no less,
how lame can you get?

00:18:01.114 --> 00:18:03.317 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Gang Leader] Ugh,
who the hell are you?

00:18:03.350 --> 00:18:05.085 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Is that you, Nerd?!

00:18:05.118 --> 00:18:07.321 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey, I managed to get
that letter finished!

00:18:07.354 --> 00:18:08.957 position:16% line:89% align:start
Thanks a lot fot he help.

00:18:08.990 --> 00:18:10.390 position:24% line:83% align:start
What the hell're
you talking about?

00:18:10.424 --> 00:18:12.894 position:19% line:83% align:start
As a thank-you I'll
help you out with this!

00:18:12.927 --> 00:18:14.862 position:7% line:89% align:start
No, dumbass, that's a bad idea!

00:18:14.896 --> 00:18:16.096 position:27% line:89% align:start
(leader growling)

00:18:16.129 --> 00:18:20.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
-(blow thuds)
-(leader groaning)

00:18:20.434 --> 00:18:21.435 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:21.468 --> 00:18:23.871 position:24% line:83% align:start
You knocked him out
cold with one punch!

00:18:23.905 --> 00:18:25.105 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who are you?

00:18:26.741 --> 00:18:30.143 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm the Tokyo Manji Gang's
First Division Captain.

00:18:31.646 --> 00:18:33.881 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm Keisuke Baji!

00:18:33.915 --> 00:18:36.283 position:33% line:89% align:start
(rock music)

00:18:40.187 --> 00:18:42.890 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu Voiceover] No
way, he took 'em all out,

00:18:42.924 --> 00:18:44.157 position:30% line:89% align:start
all by himself?

00:18:45.927 --> 00:18:48.096 position:16% line:89% align:start
Listen up, you assholes!

00:18:48.128 --> 00:18:49.631 position:24% line:83% align:start
When somebody hurts
one of our guys,

00:18:49.664 --> 00:18:51.633 position:21% line:83% align:start
the Tokyo Manji gang
comes after 'em with

00:18:51.666 --> 00:18:54.636 position:21% line:83% align:start
everything we've
got and crushes 'em!

00:18:54.669 --> 00:18:56.771 position:27% line:89% align:start
So remember that.

00:18:56.804 --> 00:18:58.338 position:13% line:89% align:start
This guy here is my friend.

00:19:00.708 --> 00:19:02.409 position:24% line:89% align:start
Lay a hand on him,

00:19:02.442 --> 00:19:05.647 position:16% line:83% align:start
and next time I'll
destroy your whole gang!

00:19:05.680 --> 00:19:06.681 position:33% line:89% align:start
'Kay, got it!

00:19:17.759 --> 00:19:20.895 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Hey, Chifuyu.
-Huh?

00:19:20.928 --> 00:19:23.263 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Like some yakisoba?
-Huh?

00:19:24.599 --> 00:19:26.266 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu Voiceover]
This is the first person

00:19:26.299 --> 00:19:27.935 position:7% line:89% align:start
I've ever had any respect for!

00:19:29.269 --> 00:19:31.639 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes, I would sir!

00:19:33.074 --> 00:19:36.209 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Baji] I live here, on the
fifth floor, stop by sometime.

00:19:36.243 --> 00:19:38.478 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu] Really, I live
here too, on the second!

00:19:38.513 --> 00:19:40.480 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Baji] Ha, well whattya know?

00:19:40.515 --> 00:19:41.949 position:10% line:89% align:start
We live in the same building.

00:19:41.983 --> 00:19:43.051 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Chifuyu] Yeah!

00:19:43.084 --> 00:19:44.184 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu Voiceover]
The first person

00:19:44.217 --> 00:19:45.853 position:16% line:89% align:start
I ever thought was cool,

00:19:45.887 --> 00:19:48.556 position:13% line:83% align:start
and the first person I ever
had any desire to follow

00:19:49.657 --> 00:19:51.793 position:27% line:89% align:start
was Keisuke Baji.

00:19:51.826 --> 00:19:53.360 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Baji] Hi Mom, I'm home.

00:19:54.361 --> 00:19:56.864 position:21% line:83% align:start
Huh, are you kidding,
we only have one left!

00:19:56.898 --> 00:19:58.166 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mom!

00:19:58.198 --> 00:20:00.500 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Chifuyu] It's okay, I-
I don't really need one.

00:20:00.535 --> 00:20:01.502 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:20:01.536 --> 00:20:03.303 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hey, let's you and I split it.

00:20:07.075 --> 00:20:09.911 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Chifuyu sobbing)

00:20:11.546 --> 00:20:12.647 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh Baji!

00:20:13.881 --> 00:20:17.719 position:16% line:89% align:start
Thanks so much, Chifuyu.

00:20:19.087 --> 00:20:21.856 position:24% line:83% align:start
You shouldn't have
said thank you!

00:20:21.889 --> 00:20:25.358 position:10% line:89% align:start
That just wasn't fair! (sobs)

00:20:25.392 --> 00:20:28.261 position:13% line:83% align:start
How the hell am I supposed
to go on now without you?

00:20:32.200 --> 00:20:33.400 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:20:35.570 --> 00:20:37.839 position:33% line:89% align:start
(soft music)

00:20:52.620 --> 00:20:55.857 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was told to expect to be
in here at least 10 years.

00:20:57.825 --> 00:20:59.326 position:16% line:89% align:start
But is even that enough?

00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:02.163 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm not running away.

00:21:02.196 --> 00:21:04.766 position:5% line:89% align:start
I need to face up to what I did.

00:21:04.799 --> 00:21:08.569 position:19% line:83% align:start
At least I learned that
much from him, and...

00:21:10.437 --> 00:21:13.908 position:10% line:83% align:start
So this time, I'm going to
actually do the right thing.

00:21:16.309 --> 00:21:18.913 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Draken] Don't kill
yourself, Kazutora.

00:21:18.946 --> 00:21:19.947 position:27% line:89% align:start
(Kazutora gasps)

00:21:22.817 --> 00:21:23.918 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Kazutora] How did you?

00:21:26.020 --> 00:21:27.287 position:21% line:89% align:start
I know what you meant

00:21:27.320 --> 00:21:29.524 position:13% line:83% align:start
because I know what
you're thinking right now.

00:21:29.557 --> 00:21:30.725 position:13% line:89% align:start
And I'll never forgive you

00:21:30.758 --> 00:21:33.426 position:16% line:83% align:start
if you take your own life
to try to make amends.

00:21:37.665 --> 00:21:41.736 position:16% line:83% align:start
But I just, I don't
know what else there is.

00:21:41.769 --> 00:21:42.837 position:24% line:89% align:start
What else can I do?

00:21:45.673 --> 00:21:47.208 position:10% line:89% align:start
I have a message from Mikey.

00:21:47.241 --> 00:21:48.441 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:21:50.211 --> 00:21:51.913 position:10% line:89% align:start
He told me to tell you this:

00:21:54.414 --> 00:21:56.383 position:7% line:89% align:start
"You're still a part of Toman."

00:22:02.924 --> 00:22:06.326 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is what you wanted
me to do, isn't it?

00:22:06.359 --> 00:22:07.360 position:35% line:89% align:start
Huh, Baji?

00:22:09.462 --> 00:22:11.999 position:21% line:89% align:start
"And I forgive you."

00:22:14.302 --> 00:22:16.971 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Kazutora sobs)

00:22:18.471 --> 00:22:23.476 position:21% line:89% align:start
(closing theme music)

00:22:24.979 --> 00:22:29.984 position:21% line:89% align:start
(singing in Japanese)

